{"seriesId":115287,"title":"怪～ayakashi～","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36577169/36577169.32836003","descriptionFirst":"伊右衛門とお岩は互いに惹かれあいながらも、お岩の父・四谷左門によって夫婦の仲を引き裂かれていた。だが、どうしても寄りを戻したい伊右衛門は、左門の命を奪ってしまう。それとは知らずに再び伊右衛門と契りを交わしたお岩であったが・・・。\n\n民谷伊右衛門:平田広明／姫川図書之助:緑川光／男（薬売り）:櫻井孝宏\n\n原作:鶴屋南北（1～4話）、泉鏡花（5～8話）／監督:今沢哲男（1～4話）、永山耕三（5～8話）、中村健治（9～11話）／脚本:小中千昭（1～4話）、坂元裕二（5～8話）、横手美智子（9～11話）\n\n©怪～ayakashi～製作委員会\n\n次話→so36577170","tags":["2006年冬アニメ","ノイタミナ","ホラー/サスペンス/推理","ドラマ/青春"],"cours":"2006-冬","colKey":"あ","relatedSeries":[],"episodes":[{"contentId":"so36577169","episodeNo":1,"title":"怪～ayakashi～　#01　東海道四谷怪談 序の幕","viewCounter":3429,"commentCounter":62,"mylistCounter":131,"lengthSeconds":1379,"startTime":"2020-04-01T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36577169/36577169.32836003"},{"contentId":"so36577170","episodeNo":2,"title":"怪～ayakashi～　#02　東海道四谷怪談 二幕目","viewCounter":1189,"commentCounter":61,"mylistCounter":2,"lengthSeconds":1380,"startTime":"2020-04-01T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36577170/36577170.46471018"},{"contentId":"so36577171","episodeNo":3,"title":"怪～ayakashi～　#03　東海道四谷怪談 三幕目","viewCounter":999,"commentCounter":60,"mylistCounter":3,"lengthSeconds":1380,"startTime":"2020-04-01T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36577171/36577171.52035547"},{"contentId":"so36577172","episodeNo":4,"title":"怪～ayakashi～　#04　東海道四谷怪談 大詰め","viewCounter":1029,"commentCounter":88,"mylistCounter":1,"lengthSeconds":1379,"startTime":"2020-04-01T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36577172/36577172.40539879"},{"contentId":"so36577173","episodeNo":5,"title":"怪～ayakashi～　#05　天守物語 序の幕","viewCounter":1114,"commentCounter":54,"mylistCounter":4,"lengthSeconds":1380,"startTime":"2020-04-01T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36577173/36577173.5302433"},{"contentId":"so36577174","episodeNo":6